84
00:05:45,044 --> 00:05:49,832
If you don't want any of these pics to show up all
over campus, hand over a computer and be quick about it.

85
00:05:49,857 --> 00:05:52,560
This is ludicrous! You forced me to touched her breasts!

86
00:05:52,585 --> 00:05:54,412
I'm innocent I tell ya!

87
00:05:54,507 --> 00:05:58,500
Wonder how many people are gonna listen to
your side of the story, you sexual harasser.

88
00:06:00,209 --> 00:06:03,523
What?! Hang on! All the club members here are witnesses!

89
00:06:03,674 --> 00:06:04,753
That's right!

90
00:06:05,269 --> 00:06:07,099
Yeah, it wasn't his fault!

91
00:06:08,138 --> 00:06:12,199
Then I'll tell everyone at school that
all you geeks ganged up on her and... ed her!

92
00:06:13,295 --> 00:06:14,740
You out of her mind or something?!

93
00:06:14,772 --> 00:06:15,600
Well, chief?

94
00:06:15,877 --> 00:06:17,737
You gonna hand it over or not?

95
00:06:17,874 --> 00:06:19,110
M-Miss Suzumiya...

96
00:06:20,827 --> 00:06:21,676
That's...!

97
00:06:32,005 --> 00:06:33,841
Take whichever one you want.

98
00:06:34,404 --> 00:06:35,549
Get up, man!

99
00:06:35,811 --> 00:06:37,009
Get a hold of yourself.

100
00:06:37,534 --> 00:06:38,423
It's gonna be okay.

101
00:06:38,448 --> 00:06:39,060
We'll figure this out...

102
00:06:39,085 --> 00:06:39,976
Don't cry.

103
00:06:40,001 --> 00:06:42,913
It's... like a bad comedy skit or something.

104
00:06:44,924 --> 00:06:46,386
Which one's the latest model?

105
00:06:46,593 --> 00:06:49,357
Give me one good reason why I should tell you that!

106
00:06:53,296 --> 00:06:54,220
That one...

107
00:06:55,523 --> 00:06:58,746
I almost forgot... I got a list from
the list from the computer store yesterday.

108
00:06:58,771 --> 00:07:00,805
It's got all the newest models on it.

109
00:07:00,996 --> 00:07:03,403
And, it looks like this computer's not listed.

110
00:07:07,406 --> 00:07:08,781
Think I'll take that one!

111
00:07:09,592 --> 00:07:12,927
Wait, that's the machine we
just bought! You can't do this!

112
00:07:16,234 --> 00:07:17,801
Take it, you thief...

113
00:07:18,275 --> 00:07:19,623
<i>Yeah, you got that right...</i>

114
00:07:19,648 --> 00:07:20,818
<i>She is a thief.</i>

115
00:07:21,135 --> 00:07:22,191
Hey, Kyon!

116
00:07:22,461 --> 00:07:23,002
Hmm?

117
00:07:23,161 --> 00:07:24,260
Could you get this?

118
00:07:24,752 --> 00:07:29,092
<i>And, just like that, Haruhi
procured a state-of-the-art computer.</i>

119
00:07:29,432 --> 00:07:33,563
<i>It was only then she learned that the
literary club wasn't wired for internet use.</i>

120
00:07:33,809 --> 00:07:37,502
<i>So she called the Computer Club over
to run a LAN cable between our rooms.</i>

121
00:07:37,527 --> 00:07:41,142
<i>She also had them set us up so that we
could connect using the school's domain.</i>

122
00:07:41,689 --> 00:07:43,522
<i>Can you say "Extortion"?</i>

123
00:07:44,184 --> 00:07:44,978
<i>Good.</i>

124
00:07:47,185 --> 00:07:49,494
Come on, what d'ya say we go back to the others?

125
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:58,676
Miss Asahina, I was thinking maybe it's best
you don't get involved with this brigade thing.

126
00:07:59,099 --> 00:08:02,024
I mean, who knows what she'll
end up doing to you if you stay?

127
00:08:04,740 --> 00:08:07,050
No, it's all right I guess.

128
00:08:11,438 --> 00:08:13,393
But you'll stay too, won't you?

129
00:08:14,209 --> 00:08:14,712
Uh...

130
00:08:17,692 --> 00:08:22,387
I guess the probability of this happening on
this particular time plane's is unavoidable.

131
00:08:22,773 --> 00:08:23,347
Huh...?

132
00:08:24,779 --> 00:08:27,758
And I'm worried about why Miss Nagato's here, too...

133
00:08:27,996 --> 00:08:28,766
What'd you say?

134
00:08:28,869 --> 00:08:29,537
Huh?

135
00:08:30,022 --> 00:08:33,026
Oh, nothing. I was just babbling.

136
00:08:33,208 --> 00:08:38,276
I might be a little inexperienced, but I
know I'm gonna get along with everyone here.

137
00:08:38,699 --> 00:08:41,790
By the way, you don't have to be so formal.

138
00:08:41,941 --> 00:08:44,554
Please just call me Mikuru if you don't mind.

139
00:08:46,286 --> 00:08:47,144
<i>Okay...</i>

140
00:08:47,573 --> 00:08:48,938
<i>So what's next...?</i>

141
00:08:51,752 --> 00:08:55,082
So, about this website, who're you gonna get to make it?

142
00:08:55,565 --> 00:08:56,446
That'd be you.

143
00:08:56,638 --> 00:08:58,706
Beats sitting around being bored all the time.

144
00:08:59,037 --> 00:09:01,254
I have to go out and find some more members now.

145
00:09:01,279 --> 00:09:04,312
Oh, and make sure you finish the
site in the next couple of days.

146
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:07,986
The club's dead in the water until
we have our site up and running.

147
00:09:13,418 --> 00:09:14,998
I'm building a website, huh?

148
00:09:16,006 --> 00:09:18,759
<i>Despite my griping, I kinda enjoyed making it.</i>

149
00:09:19,273 --> 00:09:23,887
<i>The guys from the Computer Club installed all the
software for me, so it wasn't too hard to figure out.</i>

150
00:09:24,378 --> 00:09:26,763
<i>Not a bad way to spend an otherwise boring lunch.</i>

151
00:09:27,860 --> 00:09:30,300
<i>Okay. What am I supposed to put on it?</i>

152
00:09:30,673 --> 00:09:35,650
<i>I mean, I still had absolutely no idea
what the SOS Brigade was actually going to do.</i>

153
00:09:35,815 --> 00:09:38,445
Hey, Nagato, was there anything
you wanted me to put on this site?

154
00:09:38,816 --> 00:09:39,967
No, there's not.

155
00:09:44,245 --> 00:09:46,120
<i>Not that I should get involved, but...</i>

156
00:09:46,525 --> 00:09:48,294
<i>does this girl even go to class?</i>

157
00:10:02,106 --> 00:10:04,265
Oh crap! I gotta go to class!

158
00:10:07,594 --> 00:10:08,300
Take it...

159
00:10:08,586 --> 00:10:09,896
I'll lend this to you...

160
00:10:27,268 --> 00:10:30,260
<i>Okay, I'm still not sold on this whole "Brigade" thing.</i>

161
00:10:31,006 --> 00:10:34,246
<i>So why do I find myself eagerly
commuting to the club room?</i>

162
00:10:34,865 --> 00:10:38,498
<i>Why? Is it simply what you call "habit"?</i>

163
00:10:39,538 --> 00:10:40,133
<i>Hey!</i>

164
00:10:41,989 --> 00:10:44,126
<i>These two can't be that bored, can they?</i>

165
00:10:44,682 --> 00:10:46,634
<i>Can't say I'm not bored either, but...</i>

166
00:10:47,668 --> 00:10:49,272
Where's Miss Suzumiya?

167
00:10:49,389 --> 00:10:53,052
Dunno. By the time I managed to get to
our 6th period class, she wasn't there.

168
00:10:53,248 --> 00:10:56,775
How much you wanna bet she's out there
right now extorting more gear from somebody?

169
00:10:57,985 --> 00:11:00,961
Will I be forced to do something like yesterday?

170
00:11:01,199 --> 00:11:02,852
You'll be fine, trust me.

171
00:11:02,900 --> 00:11:05,567
I'm not gonna let anything like
that happen to you ever again.

172
00:11:05,823 --> 00:11:07,367
You mean you'll protect me?!

173
00:11:07,451 --> 00:11:08,935
Oh, thank you so much!

174
00:11:08,967 --> 00:11:10,742
Guess I'll be counting on you, then!

175
00:11:10,852 --> 00:11:12,641
It's an honor to be counted on.

176
00:11:12,974 --> 00:11:15,056
Ya-hoo!

177
00:11:15,095 --> 00:11:16,347
<i>Ya... hoo?</i>

178
00:11:20,912 --> 00:11:22,404
First, take a look at this!

179
00:11:22,531 --> 00:11:26,307
"SOS Brigade... an explanation of our general policies..."

180
00:11:28,587 --> 00:11:29,919
And now, for this:

181
