187
00:11:41,322 --> 00:11:42,926
You're not the one wearing it.

188
00:11:42,951 --> 00:11:44,412
I got this outfit for Mikuru.

189
00:11:44,437 --> 00:11:45,616
Ah! What?

190
00:11:45,691 --> 00:11:47,264
A bunny girl costume.

191
00:11:47,297 --> 00:11:49,935
But... how... how am I supposed to...?

192
00:11:50,092 --> 00:11:51,721
Come on! Put it on! Get dressed!

193
00:11:51,746 --> 00:11:53,007
But I don't want to!

194
00:11:53,032 --> 00:11:54,930
Shut up and strip! Come on, girl!

195
00:11:54,955 --> 00:11:56,136
Nooo!

196
00:11:56,161 --> 00:11:58,007
Hey, Suzumiya! Stop it!

197
00:11:58,157 --> 00:12:01,000
Please, no! No, don't look!

198
00:12:01,234 --> 00:12:02,328
Quit struggling!

199
00:12:02,566 --> 00:12:04,375
But I don't wanna put it on!

200
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:06,840
Move your arm! Let's go, Mikuru, take it off!

201
00:12:06,865 --> 00:12:07,927
Take it off!

202
00:12:14,254 --> 00:12:17,232
Noo... don't...

203
00:12:18,115 --> 00:12:20,013
Let me take it off myself!

204
00:12:20,331 --> 00:12:22,133
No! Noo!

205
00:12:23,429 --> 00:12:24,688
You can come in now!

206
00:12:24,713 --> 00:12:26,468
<i>She's like an evil overlord.</i>

207
00:12:28,506 --> 00:12:31,690
Well? Think we'll get some attention now or what?

208
00:12:31,715 --> 00:12:33,330
Don't think that'll be a problem.

209
00:12:33,719 --> 00:12:35,051
Nagato wasn't into it?

210
00:12:35,076 --> 00:12:37,196
Nah, I could only afford two of 'em.

211
00:12:37,221 --> 00:12:39,851
I got the deluxe set, so they were expensive.

212
00:12:39,876 --> 00:12:41,462
Where'd you buy these things...?

213
00:12:41,487 --> 00:12:42,949
I got 'em online.

214
00:12:43,195 --> 00:12:43,977
I see.

215
00:12:44,802 --> 00:12:46,201
Well, we'll be going now.

216
00:12:46,931 --> 00:12:48,676
Come on, Mikuru, let's head out.

217
00:12:48,701 --> 00:12:49,856
No, I don't wanna...

218
00:12:50,090 --> 00:12:51,444
Nooo!

219
00:12:52,828 --> 00:12:54,958
Let's go! Yeah!

220
00:12:56,926 --> 00:12:57,752
<i>Sorry...</i>

221
00:12:58,204 --> 00:13:01,146
<i>Honestly though, that outfit's killing me right now.</i>

222
00:13:01,923 --> 00:13:04,226
<i>My passion's going through the roof here...</i>

223
00:13:18,893 --> 00:13:20,584
