00:13:22,937 --> 00:13:25,040
<i>It's still warm from their body heat...</i>

225
00:13:29,375 --> 00:13:32,743
<i>"The SOS Brigade: An explanation of our general policies.</i>

226
00:13:33,005 --> 00:13:37,055
