mysteries that freak us out!

234
00:13:58,975 --> 00:14:00,453
"Please keep that in mind."

235
00:14:00,730 --> 00:14:04,336
<i>I think I'm starting to understand
the reason for this brigade's existence.</i>

236
00:14:09,733 --> 00:14:11,369
They piss me off so much!

237
00:14:11,394 --> 00:14:13,294
I mean, what's with those stupid teachers?!

238
00:14:13,319 --> 00:14:14,434
They're always butting in!

239
00:14:14,459 --> 00:14:16,572
So what happened out there? Did you guys get into trouble?

240
00:14:16,597 --> 00:14:21,974
Unbelievable! We passed out half our flyers and
